;;     짜잔 투움바 파스타입니다. 비주얼은 좀 비슷해보이나요? ㅎㅎ   신랑에게 요렇게 놓임새 해서 상차림 하니까~ 아웃백이 안부럽다고 하던데^^;;   샐러드라도 하나 같이 놓아줄걸 그랬나봐요^^;;   투움바 파스타 비슷한 맛인것 같긴 해요.   좀 매콤하면서.. 뭐랄까..저 크림소스에 계속 막 뭔가를 먹고 싶어요. 스푼으로 저 소스 퍼먹고 싶어지고~ 빵 찍어먹고 싶어지는..그런 희안한 마력의^^;;   암튼 맛나더라구용..   생크림만 숙성된다면 정말 만들기는 쉬워요. 추천추천~   주말 별식으로 추천드려보아용^^","images":["http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141121_113/inalove_1416524421858YJrtc_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_384_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141121_88/inalove_1416524422252iFht9_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_360_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141121_26/inalove_1416524422546cXAHe_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_362_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141121_152/inalove_1416524422856zQ1N2_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_364_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141121_278/inalove_1416524423161hwLUr_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_366_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141121_259/inalove_1416524423408wfv8B_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_370_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141121_265/inalove_1416524423697iXFxm_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_373_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141121_240/inalove_1416524424005djK1f_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_375_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141121_99/inalove_1416524424309S6jfF_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_384_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141121_58/inalove_14165244246519p2R8_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_390_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141121_164/inalove_1416524425125vxNWC_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_397_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141121_300/inalove_1416524425425uAvgX_JPEG/%BB%E7%C1%F8_399_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141121_270/inalove_1416524425849V24IV_JPEG/%B0%F8%B0%A8%B7%CE%B0%ED_%BA%B9%BB%E7.jpg?type="],"nickname":"뽀로롱꼬마마녀","id":"뽀로롱꼬마마녀","comment_no":0,"like":0}
